{"tid":1933164,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"置業的抉擇 私樓定已補地價居屋","createTime":"2020-03-19T06:43:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-12T02:49:38.000Z","uid":154984,"like":42,"dislike":121,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"2d288de4a16157c90ba36fc095121c8ac11f1e98","tid":1933164,"uid":154984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T06:43:18.000Z","msg":"想問下大家有咩意見自住，地鐵沿線，基本上係隔離咁滯，價錢來講三房已補地價居屋貴1球<br />\n<br />\n1. 私樓20年樓齡，有會所，各方面都保養得好，有大露台450尺兩房有廁所有梗廚，不過真正室內面積減露台就變得相對細<br />\n<br />\n2. 居屋25年樓齡，好處係可以買到三房600尺，仲有兩個廁所<br />\n<br />\n兩間屋買咗基本上都要重新裝修<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />私樓點都係唔同啲有會所，成個環境都high class D<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />已補地價居屋住得舒舒服服"},{"pid":"c685996ccf51a110a0b2d3afd552b2512ffc7175","tid":1933164,"uid":244152,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T06:47:23.000Z","msg":"居<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n樓主邊區居"},{"pid":"6e73651298ddba4451fe68a9e406c89e4a143b2b","tid":1933164,"uid":47658,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T06:49:33.000Z","msg":"一定有大住大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7235ddd7213a9bac7e38e965d921be2bed372fd0","tid":1933164,"uid":154984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T06:59:28.000Z","msg":"支持私樓嘅可唔可以講下點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e180caa09935ecb453edd45569a9f8a3bb92caaa","tid":1933164,"uid":7452,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T07:03:10.000Z","msg":"私樓區高質 居屋區近公屋拉低晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58c1fe42b4676fa2b3b77342d5ea42b98dfc17f8","tid":1933164,"uid":154984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c685996ccf51a110a0b2d3afd552b2512ffc7175","tid":1933164,"uid":244